                    "company": "University of Cambridge",
                    "description": "CLOVER was an experiment to measure the B-mode polarization of the Cosmic Microwave Background with the aim of detecting primordial gravitational waves.  I completed the testing of the full set of CLOVER detector modules, documented our team's technical achievements, and published the test results to close out the CLOVER project.",
